tafsir[37]{c,v,t}:
  45,1,"Haa, Miim. Yewtere fii sugu …óee kalfe yawtiino ka cortewol Al baqarah."
  45,2,"Jippagol Alqur'aana, ko immorde ka Allah, Foolu…óo Mo fooletake On, √ëee√±u…óo e tagu Mun e kattal Mun e toppitagol Mun."
  45,3,"Pellet, hino e kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin, tinndinay…ói kattal e gootaagu Allah ngun, wonannde gom…óim…ìe …ìen. Tawde ko …ìen taskorta maandeeji …óin."
  45,4,"Hino e tagugol on ngol kadi, onon yim…ìe …ìen, immorde e to…ì…ìere maniiyu, refti huyre, refti he…ó…óere, e ngun tagu ngu Allah saaki ka leydi hino ruuga, ko maandeeji wonii e …óum fow, wonannde yim…ìe yananaa…ìe wonnde ko Allah woni tagu…óo On."
  45,5,"Wonii kadi e luutongol jemma e √±alorma ngol, e kon ko Allah jippiniri ka kammu, immorde e ndiyam, O wuurnitiri …óam leydi ndin, fewndo ndi yoorunoo ndi alaa pu…ói, e firlitagol keneeli …óin, yiltindira …ói senngo kala, tuma woo, fii nafa mon, ko maandeeji non, wonannde yim…ìe haqqiloo…ìe …ìen. ∆Åe dallinora …óum, e wootin…óingol Allah ngol, e wonnde Himo ha…ótani ummitingol, O ha…ótani huunde kala."
  45,6,"∆äin ko maandeeji e hujjaaji …ói Men janngirta e dow maa…óa, an Nulaa…óo, e hoore goonga. Si tawii …ìe gom…óinaali yewtere Allah e hujjaaji mun jippinaa…ói e Jeyaa…óo Makko on, haray ko yewtere honnde goo …ìe gom…óinoyta?"
  45,7,"Halkaare e lepte Allah woodanii kala …óuu…óu…óo fenaande e bakktuuji !"
  45,8,"On geddo hino nana Aayeeje Allah …óen ka Alqur'aana hino janngee e dow makko, refti o duumoo e geddi e keeferaaku makko, o townitanoo jokkugol goonga kan, wa si tawii o nanaano …óen Aayeeje janngaa…óe e dow makko. Awa an Nulaa…óo, humpitu on bone makko laakara, …óum le ko lepte muusu…óe hino habbitii mo ton."
  45,9,"Si go…ó…óum hewtii mo e Alqur'aana, o jogitora …óum jalnori makko. ∆Åen sifor…ìe ngol jalkitugol Alqur'aana, hino woodani lepte hoynooje, √ëalnde Darngal."
  45,10,"Jahannama hino yeeso ma…ì…ìe, habbitii …ìe laakara. Jawle …óe …ìe faggitinoo duncanoytaa…ìe huunde ka Allah, wanaa sanamuuji …ói …ìe jogitinoo rewetee…ói …óin gaanin Allah, woni ko duncanoyta …ìe. Hino woodani …ìe √ëalnde Darngal, lepte maw…óe."
  45,11,"Ndee deftere nde Men jippini e Nulaa…óo Amen on Muhammadu, ko …óowoore e goonga. ∆Åen yeddu…ìe non Aayeeje Joomi ma…ì…ìe …óen, hino woodani …ìe lepte bon…óe muusu…óe."
  45,12,"Ko Alla gooto O woni eeltan…óo mon- ono yim…ìe- maaya ngo ngam laa…óe ndiyam ndoga e hengo, haa …óa…ì…ìon e …ìural makko e nooneeji paggitaa…óe dagii…óe, mbela joo njetton neemaaji Alla e dow mon."
  45,13,"Alla mbo senaade woodani eeltanii mon denndaangal ko woni e kammuuji hono naange e lewru e koode, e ko woni e leydi hono caatli e le…ó…óe e montaanji eken, wonii e eeltude …óiin noon dallilaajim baawka Alla e ngootaagu Makko, wonande yim…ìe miijatoo…ìe kaawisaaji makko …ói …ìe teskoo…ói."
  45,14,"Maakan aan Nulaa…óo, …ìeen goon…óin…ì Alla e nulal Nullaa…óo Makko : yo…ìe njaafa …ìeen heefere…ìe bon…ìe e mum en …ìe nganndu…óa paalaaka neemaaji Alla e lepte makko e dow mum en, Ma Alla yo…ì goon…óin…ìe muny…ìe e heefr…ìe jaggit…ìe ko…ìe paggittono e golle nder aduna;"
  45,15,"Kala gollu…ó…óo golle lobbe ko hoore mum o gollani, Alla na yondani e golle mum he, kala kadi mo golli golle bon…óe ko lepte …óe ngonata e dow mum, bone golle mum loratah Alla, refti koto Alla …ìe nduttoto nyande darngon gooto fof yo…ìe ko haandi ko."
  45,16,"Ko goongo Min njonnii Banii Israa*iil Tawreet e senndude hakkunde aade en min wa…ói ko …ìuri heewde e Annabaa…ìe ko Annabi Ibraahiima njalti yo jam e kisal ngon e mum, Min ngarsikini …ìe e nooneeji laa…ì…ói, Min …ìurni…ìe e yim…ìe jamaanu mum en."
  45,17,"Min tootti…ìe dallillaaji …ìanngu…ói ceerndooji hakkunde goongo e fenaande, …ìe luuraani si wonah caggal nde hujjaaji neleede Muhamed pawii e ma…ì…ìe, alah fof ko foo…ói…ìe e ngal luural si wonah bewre e reer…óude e laamu kam e koongu, Joomo noo Aan Nulaa…óo na seernda hakkunde mum en ko…ìe yeddandiratno ka aduna, O seernda jom goongo e jom fenaande."
  45,18,"Refti Min mba…óma e laawol e sunna e dow yamiroore Amen nde Min njamiri annabaa…ìe adii…ìe, nodda e Iimaan e golle lobbe, rew o sariya, woto belaa…óe …ìeen …ìe nganndah goonga, belaa…óe ma…ì…ìe na majjina…ìe gaa e goonga."
  45,19,"Pellet …ìeen …ìe nganndah goonga …ìe curantaa Ma lepte Alla hay huunde si a rewii belaa…óe ma…ì…ìe, toonyoo…ìe seertu…ìe laabi yogo e mum en wallat yogo goo, …ìe mballandira e dow juul…ìe, Alla noon wallat hul…ìe Ko…ìe ciini jamirooje makko deenii ka…óaa…óe Makko."
  45,20,"O quraana kombo gite …óe yim…ìe njiirata goongo e peewal faade e goongo, e yurmeende wonande yananaa…ìe, sabu ko e mammbo …ìe peewrata faade e laawol poocingol ngam Joomi mum en welee…ìe, O naatna…ìe aljanna, O deestina…ìe yiite."
  45,21,"Mbela …ìeen faggitirii…ìe ter…óe mum en keefeeru e goopi cikkat ma Min mba…ó njo…ìdi mum en hono njo…ìdi …ìeen gollu…ìe golle lobbe, …ìe ngoon…óini, …ìe pota aduna e laakara? kaanii √±aawoore mum en."
  45,22,"O tagri kammuuji e leydi √±ee√±al timmungal, O tagiraani…ói fijirde, e ngam O yo…ìa kala fittaandu kondu faggino ko boni wolla ko lobbi, Alla toonyataa…ìe ustude mo∆¥∆¥i mum en ma …ìeydude bon…ói mum en."
  45,23,"Ndaar -aan nulaado- faade e oon dew…óo belaa…óe mum o wa…ói…óe hono dewetoo…óo mbo o lunndataaka, Alla majjanii mbo e ganndal ummaade e makko, sabu hombo haandi e majjineede, O ommbi …ìernde makko o nanatah nangol naftaraade, O muuri ndaar…óe makko haa o sutataako goonga, hombo hawrinta oon e goonga caggal de Alla majjani mbo? Mbela on miccataaka lorlo rewde belaa…óe, e nafoore rewde sariya."
  45,24,"Heefaree…ìe yeddu…ìe ummital wii: Nguurndam alah si wonah nguurndam amen aduna …óam, nguurndam alah caggal …óaam, njiirle na maaya nduttataaka, jiirle kadi nguura, alah ko warata min si wonah lomtandirde jemma e nyalawma, …ìe ngalah ganndal ko…ìe njeddi ko ummital, …ìe ngonah si wonah sikkoo…ìe, te sikke nafatah goonga hay ndiga;"
  45,25,"Si aayeeje Amen njanngaama e sirku…ìe yeddu…ìe ummital, …ìe nda√±atah hujja mbo kujjinorto si wonah wiide Nulaa…óo yo o his e wondii…ìe makko: nguurtinane min baabiraa…ìe amen si on ngonii goon…óu…ìe e ko nodditta…óon wonde ma min ummita caggal maayde amen:"
  45,26,"Maakan…ìe Aan Nulaa…óo: Alla na wuurna mon e takde mon refti O wara mon, refti O renndina on caggal maayde mon faade darorde nyalngu darnga ngam haasbo e njo…ìdi, oon nyalawma sikke alah e gargol mammbo, kono ko …ìuri heewde e yim…ìe nganndah, ko …óum wa…ói …ìe keblorantaaka …óum golle mo∆¥∆¥e."
  45,27,"Ko Alla tan laamu kammuuji e leydi ngoodani, alah pot…óo reweede e goonga mbo wona Alla, nyande darnga darii Alla ummitini maay…ìe ngam hasbeede e njo…ìdi nyande heen de meerantee…ìe rewatnoo…ìe ko wonah Alla yahatnoo…ìe ngam bonnude goonga cemmbina meere perta."
  45,28,"Ha…óa yiya - aan nulaa…óo- e oon nyalawma kala lenyol na gurfanii e koppi mum na fadi ko wa…óate, kala lenyol na nodde e deftere golle mum nde malaykaaji binndooji mbinnduno, nguu √±allngu ma on njo…ìe ko ngollatna…óon e aduna fofti ko lobbum wolla ko bon…óum."
  45,29,"Ndee ko deftere Amen- nde malaykaaji amen mbinndatno golle mon- honde seedoo e mon goonga njanngee nde, Min ngoniina yamiroo…ìe malaykaaji binndooji nde mbinndata golle mon ka aduna."
  45,30,"Tawi ko …ìeen goon…óin…ìe …ìe ngolli golle mo∆¥∆¥e Joomi mum en ma O naatnu…ìe aljana e yurmeende mum, ndiin njo…ìdi ndi Alla totti…ìe woni malal laa…ìngal ngal mal malal go…óngal waawah …ìadaade."
  45,31,"Tawii ko been yeddube Alla be wi*nee woynude …ìe: Mbele aayeeje Am njanngetanaake e mon mawnakinadon dow iimanaagal, gondon yim…ìe bon…ìe, paggitadon heeefeeru e goopi."
  45,32,"Si…ìe mbi*aama:pellet fodoore Alla fodani jiyaabe mum wonde ma O ummitibe O yobabe ko goonga mbo alah sikke, darnga ko goonga sikke alah heen ngoolonee mbo, mbi*on: Min nganndah o darnga, min cikkiti sikke loodo wonde ma mbo ar, min njananaaka gargol mammba."
  45,33,"Fee√±ani…ìe boneeji golle mum en nder aduna ummorde e keefaraagu e goopi, lepte …óe…ìe njalkitatno tellii e mum en …óe…ìe njeertinteno e mum."
  45,34,"Alla daalani…ìe: hannde Min acca on e yiite hono no yejjatir…óon √±alngu mon hannde ngu, on keblanaani ngu iimaan e golle lobbe, ko yiite woni √±ii…ìirde, on ngalah balla diiwanoowo mon le…ìte."
  45,35,"Le…ìte …óe …óe lepte…óon sabu ko njaggirno …óon aayeeje Alla …óe saboote e jalkitde, nguurndam aduna …óam hodiri mon dakamme e tuuyooji majjam, hannde …ìe heefer…ìe jalkitatnoo…ìe aayeeje Alla njaltatah yiite, …ìe keddato e henge haa pooma, …ìe nduttetaake e nguurndam aduna haa …ìe ngolla golle lobbe, Joomi mum en weletaake …ìe."
  45,36,"Ko Alla tan woodani jettoode, Jom kammuuji e leydi, Jom denndaangal tagu."
  45,37,"Ina woodani Mbo teddungal e manngu nder kammuuji e leydi, kanko woni pool…óo mbo gooto foolatah, nyeenya e tagu makko e hoddira makko e jiilgol makko e sariya makko."
